            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "有代理分析樓市小陽春已經出現",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15575631&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">踏入新一年，本港樓市氣氛持續回暖，綜合市場統計，過去兩日市場共錄得超過310宗一手成交，為近8個月以來最旺的周末。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240524_CR_source_web_Landscape_01.jpeg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240524_CR_source_web_Landscape_01.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新地西沙住宅項目周六開賣213伙價單單位，即日全數沽清。發展商加推兩張價單，合共211伙。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產住宅部總裁陳永傑指出，去年樓價累計升4.7%，年初整體市場氣氛樂觀，市場認為樓市進入升浪，相信「小陽春」已經出現。他估計，今個月一手成交有望突破兩千宗。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">陳永傑又指，過去11年辣招打擊二手市場，現已全面鬆綁，有助買家入市，銀行承造按揭貸款亦較積極。至於二手業主憧憬未來樓市進一步造好，議價空間明顯收窄，現時二手放盤叫價普遍升5%至8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15575631-%e6%9c%89%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90%e6%a8%93%e5%b8%82%e5%b0%8f%e9%99%bd%e6%98%a5%e5%b7%b2%e7%b6%93%e5%87%ba%e7%8f%be-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240820_FI_source_licensed_HKProperty_shutterstock_704-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 13:50:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
