            "title": "台股全日回吐0.42%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台股連升3日後回吐，今早低開後全程報跌，收報30810點，跌131點或0.42%。</p>\n</div>",
