        {
            "title": "李寧上季銷售點零售流水按年錄低單位數跌幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">李寧(02331)公布，截至去年底止季度，李寧銷售點(不包括李寧YOUNG)於整個平台的零售流水，按年錄得低單位數下降。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/02331-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/02331-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以渠道劃分，線下渠道(包括零售及批發)錄得中單位數下降，其中零售(直接經營)渠道錄得低單位數下降，批發(特許經銷商)渠道錄得中單位數下降；電子商務虛擬店舖業務則持平。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至2025年底該公司在中國的銷售網絡上，李寧銷售點數量(不包括李寧YOUNG)共計6091個，按季淨減少41個，全年淨減少26個。在淨減少的26個銷點售中，零售業務淨減少59個，批發業務淨增加33個。李寧YOUNG共計1518個，按季淨增加38個，全年淨增加50個。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584395-%e6%9d%8e%e5%af%a7%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e9%bb%9e%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%b5%81%e6%b0%b4%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%8c%84%e4%bd%8e%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%95%b8%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20231025_FI_source-web_02331.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 12:25:37",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱兩萬七得復失 恒指跌147點報26852點 阿里系回吐 攜程曾再挫逾21%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股連升4日後於今早跟隨外圍向下，於兩萬七關口得而復失，近日強勢的阿里孖寶亦回吐，攜程(09961)更一度挫逾21%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230719_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230719_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數輕今早微低開27點，初段曾迅速轉升重越27000點，升幅一度擴大至207點，高見27206點後動力消退，於上午10時半前失守27000點並轉跌，早市後段最低報26844點，跌155點且續於低位徘徊。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230719_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230719_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：攜程官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230719_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：攜程官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午收報26852點，跌147點或0.55%。恒生科技指數今早更全程報跌，收挫107點或1.83%，報5800點；國企指數則跌64點或0.69%，報9251點。主板半日成交1638.97億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌85點，報26889點，高水37點。科指期貨跌94點，報5809點，高水9點。國指期貨跌47點，報9263點，高水12點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241009_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨午央視新聞報道指，近期市場監管總局根據前期核查，依據《中華人民共和國反壟斷法》，對攜程涉嫌濫用市場支配地位實施壟斷行為立案調查。其後攜程在黑板報證實有關消息，表明將積極配合監管部門調查，全面落實監管要求。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">攜程昨天已以全日低位收市，挫6.49%，在藍籌表現排包尾。該股今早跌勢未止，最低見446元，再挫21.69%；中午收報457.6元，仍跌19.65%，續為表現最差恒指成分股，成交急增至99.83億元。單是攜程，已拖低恒指43點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">有券商估計，若攜程在調查中被判違反《中華人民共和國反壟斷法》，罰款最多可以達數十億元。瑞銀指出，以往市監局由啟動調查至最終裁決，一般需時4至6個月；處罰包括罰款、實施補救措施、行政指導及持續合規義務。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：攜程官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">瑞銀指出，如要罰款，金額一般為上年度境內營業額的3%至4%，位於中國《反壟斷法》規定的1%至10%範圍內。按估算，攜程可能面臨3.92億至39億元人民幣的罰款，相當於2026財年非公認會計準則淨利潤的2%至18%。摩根大通也估計，若攜程在事件上被判罰判，金額或介乎6億至62億元人幣。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">近日支撐大市的阿里系，今早亦掉頭轉跌，其中阿里巴巴(09988)今早宣布千問App重大升級，又披露上線兩個月內月度活躍用戶已破億，股價依然跟隨大市反覆下跌。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴今早低開0.1元後曾轉升，最高報170.1元，升0.65%，未幾便重新轉跌，最低報163.1元，跌3.46%；該股中午收報164元，跌2.96%，拖低恒指逾66點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同系阿里健康(00241)回吐幅度更明顯，中午收報7.12元，挫8.48%，在藍籌中表現排尾二。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584370-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83%e5%be%97%e5%be%a9%e5%a4%b1-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c147%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126852%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e7%b3%bb%e5%9b%9e",
