        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市反覆再回 熱炒股紛回吐",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深北證交所昨天中午宣布升融資保證金比例，持續影響A股氣氛，內地股市今早反覆再回，多隻早前熱炒的股份亦份紛紛回吐。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230904_FI_source-web_shenzhem-stock-exchange_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230904_FI_source-web_shenzhem-stock-exchange_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開19點後曾迅速反彈倒升，但在升6點、見4133點便乏力再上，未幾重新轉跌，且於後段反覆尋底，曾失守4100點，最低報4097點，跌28點點；滬指中午收報4101點，跌24點或0.6%，半日成交7460.53億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指早市走勢類同，分別在於半日低位於初段已出現，最低14155點，跌93點，其後亦曾反彈倒升，最高報14328點，升80點，中段開始進入爭持局面，尾段跌幅再擴大；深指中午收報14186點，跌62點或0.44%，成交1.13萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌10點或0.23%，收報4731點；創業板指數跌34點或1.02%，報3314點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多隻早前價量齊升的熱門股今早顯著回吐，藍色光標(300058.SZ)挫 %，中國衛星(600118.SH)跌停板，中國衛通(601698.SH)、航天電子(600879.SH)均跌超過9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同樣曾熱炒的金風科技(02208)A股(002202.SZ)也跌停板，報30.04元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：金風科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/09/20230906_FI_source-web_金風科技1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金風科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/09/20230906_FI_source-web_金風科技1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：金風科技官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，有色金屬板塊則逆市揚升，江西銅業(00658)A股(600362.SH)升5.68%，報63.2元；洛陽鉬業(03993)A股(603993.SH)升3.43%，報24.1元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升2.91%，報47.7元。鋰業股反彈，贛鋒鋰業(01772)A股(002460.SZ)漲5.01%，報72.52元；天齊鋰業(09696)A股(002466.SZ)升2.83%，報61.51元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584255-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e5%86%8d%e5%9b%9e-%e7%86%b1%e7%82%92%e8%82%a1%e7%b4%9b%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90",
