        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴千問App月度活躍用戶破億 股價今早隨大市反覆倒跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)今早宣布千問App重大升級，又披露上線兩個月內月度活躍用戶已破億，但公司今早股價依然跟隨大市反覆倒跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早稍微低開0.1元後，初段曾倒升1.1元或0.65%，最高見170.1元，其後再掉頭下滑，最低報163.1元，跌3.49%；截至上午約10時53分報165元，仍跌2.37%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584050-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%8d%83%e5%95%8fapp%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%a6%e6%b4%bb%e8%ba%8d%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b6%e7%a0%b4%e5%84%84-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e9%9a%a8%e5%a4%a7%e5%b8%82",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 10:55:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股再重越兩萬七 金融股領漲 攜程跌勢未止",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股低開後迅速倒升，港股氣氛隨之好轉，再度重越兩國七關口，金融股是升市主要功臣，攜程(09961)則跌勢未止。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_攜程集團09961-2-官網影片截圖.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_攜程集團09961-2-官網影片截圖.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：攜程集團官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約10時05分，恒生指數報27115點，升115點或0.43%，早前最高曾見27206點；恒生科技指數則跌0.66%，恒生金融分類指數升0.96%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">攜程涉壟斷遭市場監管總局立案調查，該股昨天低收成藍籌包尾後，今早在大成交下急挫，最低曾見446元，挫21.69%；跌幅暫略為收窄至18.31%，報465.2元，成交已近61億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多隻藍籌金融股造好，是支撐升市的主力。友邦(01299)、港交所(00388)、建設銀行(00939)、工商銀行(01398)均升逾1%，中國平安(02318)更漲約2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15583898-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%86%8d%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e6%bc%b2-%e6%94%9c%e7%a8%8b%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e6%9c%aa%e6%ad%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 10:15:31",
